Each station has a different temperature based on location and elevation.  =
Station #2 is far less than Station #1 based on elevation.  Station #1 is 9=
5 F and Station #2 is 90 F.  Station #2 is over 7000 feet while Station #1 =
is around 5000 feet.  The drop is quick because Needles is around 500 feet.=
  There is a 2000 feet swing between stations starting from Station #4 west=
. =20

