in general you have an additional 3% HP available for every 10 deg F below =
95 deg at each station.  During the summer Stations 1, 3, and 4 are already=
 at MAOP and would not matter.  At station 2 the 10 deg would gain 5 mmscfd=
 to Phoenix and mayby 3 mmscfd to Ca.   We will have run additional models =
to verify offcases.




